{"tid":1293632,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全城杯葛警察大行動","createTime":"2019-07-07T16:28:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-07T20:50:14.000Z","uid":159736,"like":117,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1225e5fc25d72295d68eb324f969d33283e56976","tid":1293632,"uid":159736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:28:18.000Z","msg":"餐廳食肆酒吧攝影鋪婚紗鋪零售店補習社洗衫鋪教會車房老師社工交友app 咩都好 希望各界響應<br />\n唔做佢生意，亦都唔做佢屋企人生意，<br />\n買衫全部無size  食魚蛋河話河賣唒 轉魚蛋面就魚蛋賣哂 要咩無咩 再唔係就私人加料俾佢 <br />\n幫佢啲仔女補習既就教錯哂佢，一係全部答唔知 <br />\n學校，社工收到警察家屬既case 全部去哂waiting <br />\n警察犯左十誡，踢佢出教會，唔好俾機會佢溝仔渦溝女，要溝就番屯門溝番佢地個娜娜同老淫蟲。<br />\n<br />\n打人打得咁開心丫拿，唔show委任證丫拿，<br />\n叫人走又拉9人丫拿，幫手擋鏡頭打人丫拿。<br />\n<br />\n我要佢地後悔！！！<br />\n再唔收斂 包庇同胞就成班一齊無好日子過!!!"},{"pid":"f5f44280cff20862c5b619b0926e449d8cf58c95","tid":1293632,"uid":154054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:29:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68184af3b42d8d7e420a1719b235e5c500a4e405","tid":1293632,"uid":268548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80ebb46d091d4af5250669c73ca1030e17977bcc","tid":1293632,"uid":159736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:42:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"252662a4fd33ec4f9b5cbb89d71202aec5cea94e","tid":1293632,"uid":159736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:49:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"974d7708121c32a501fa7c8b0c5800c78f2e79ff","tid":1293632,"uid":49312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:49:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6571de09c11b4e0fa50aa6fca2d5fe36c427e35c","tid":1293632,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T16:50:15.000Z","msg":"一直都...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n補習<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d66adb911d403f946859c882283f41e333fec470","tid":1293632,"uid":107686,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"c